{"tid":1582313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 上水連儂牆有大陸佬徘徊懷疑為聽日行動視察","createTime":"2019-09-20T04:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T04:09:16.000Z","uid":310207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fad3e1edf9f2599a7fb3a0c80f3333ed22bb3032","tid":1582313,"uid":310207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:01:13.000Z","msg":"重申一次，何君堯聽日個清連儂牆嘅行動係<span style=\"color: red;\">無取消</span>，大家唔好掉以輕心要乖乖地留返喺屋企啊<br />\n<br />\n事源小弟今朝九點去mos burger買早餐食，經過上水黨鐵站天橋嘅連儂牆，見到兩個大陸男人右耳帶住個鬼死咁大嘅免提耳機(狗用嗰隻)，鬼鬼祟祟咁喺連儂牆範圍徘徊。我都唔敢肯定<br />\n係大陸佬定係上水鄉黑佬，因為個人認為佢地啲樣同啲體味係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最恐怖嘅係，我而家十二點(三個鐘之後)搭黨鐵返黨大，嗰兩個男人企係同一個位置，繼續徘徊，即係佢地喺連儂牆徘徊左三個鐘無郁過，帶著個濕鳩耳機唔知想做乜撚野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dprt1Pk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDprt1Pk.jpg&h=49379a31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外一個人企埋左影唔到<br />\n上水巴打經過可以監察下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fa8f3caf65e1121d86ee22c2671dc850df24ce","tid":1582313,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:02:21.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8vzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=8ef7d7c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me